[{"id":"VR802599","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a point P midway between two perpendicular wires that are separated by a distance of 4 centimeters. The wire above point P is horizontal and carries a current of I sub 1 equals 3 amps to the right, and the wire below point P carries a current of I sub 2 equals 4 amps out of the page.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR802599.g02.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two long straight wires carry currents as shown. Wire <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> carries a current of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 amps\"><math alttext=\"3 amps\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> to the right and Wire <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, positioned <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 centimeters\"><math alttext=\"4 centimeters\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi>cm</mi></math></span></span> away from Wire <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>, carries a current of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 amps\"><math alttext=\"4 amps\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> out of the page. What is the magnitude of the magnetic field at Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></math></span></span>, the midpoint between the two wires?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR802599_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\"><math alttext=\"1 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>–</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>T</mtext></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2.5 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\"><math alttext=\"2.5 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2.5</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>–</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>T</mtext></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"5 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\"><math alttext=\"5 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>–</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>T</mtext></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"7 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\"><math alttext=\"7 times 10 raised to the negative 5 power tesla\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>7</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mo>–</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>T</mtext></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]